  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个扫描器的状态机，核心问题是处理那些以##开头的指令行。扫描器一开始是Idle状态，遇到## directive就进入CollectingDocs。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "CollectingDocs",
        "## directive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Idle是起始状态。那如果扫描器在Idle时遇到普通非文档行呢？是留在Idle还是报错？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Non-doc line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "留在Idle，直接忽略掉。只有遇到## directive才会触发状态转移。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Idle",
        "Non-doc line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Idle自环加上Non-doc line。现在CollectingDocs内部能处理哪些指令？我注意到有## !var和## !alias。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CollectingDocs",
        "## !var",
        "## !alias"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，但关键是## !category——它会跳转到CategorySet状态，这个状态很特殊，category是sticky的，会应用到后续所有target直到被修改。另外## !file会跳到FileDoc状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CollectingDocs",
        "CategorySet",
        "FileDoc",
        "## !category",
        "## !file",
        "sticky",
        "currentCategory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "FileDoc和CategorySet最终都要能回到Idle或CollectingDocs吧？特别是target line出现时。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FileDoc",
        "CategorySet",
        "Idle",
        "CollectingDocs",
        "target line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。FileDoc遇到content line就回Idle；CategorySet和CollectingDocs遇到target line都回Idle。但FileDoc和CategorySet遇到## doc line时，都要回到CollectingDocs继续收集。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FileDoc",
        "content line",
        "Idle",
        "CategorySet",
        "CollectingDocs",
        "target line",
        "## doc line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构清楚了。我需要在CollectingDocs旁边加个注释，说明pending state包含pendingDocs、pendingVars、pendingAliases和sticky的currentCategory。CategorySet那边也标注一下sticky特性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CollectingDocs",
        "CategorySet",
        "pendingDocs",
        "pendingVars",
        "pendingAliases",
        "currentCategory",
        "sticky"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，CategorySet本身也可以自环——如果连续遇到## !category，应该留在CategorySet更新category，而不是报错。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CategorySet",
        "## !category"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，给CategorySet加上自环。这样整个状态流转就完整了，从[*]起始到Idle，再在各状态间根据指令类型跳转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Idle",
        "CategorySet",
        "CollectingDocs",
        "FileDoc"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
